A host-parasite
pair in which the
parasite mushroom has taken over the
host bug. Prefers
damp places.

A host-parasite
pair in which the
parasite mushroom has taken over the
host bug. Prefers
damp places.

The bug host is
drained of energy
by the mushrooms on its back. They
appear to do all
the thinking.

It stays mostly in
dark, damp places,
the preference not of the bug, but
of the big mush
rooms on its back.

The larger the
mushroom on its
back grows, the stronger the mush
room spores it
scatters.

When nothing's
left to extract
from the bug, the mushrooms on its
back leave spores
on the bug's egg.

PARASECT is known to infest large trees
en masse and drain nutrients from the
lower trunk and roots. When an infested tree dies, they move
onto another tree all at once.

Le gros champignon sur son dos contrle
le Pokmon. Lampignon et Parasect
se disputent souvent un mme territoire.

Parasek wird von dem Pilz auf seinen Rcken

La gran seta en su lomo lo controla. A menudo

The large mushroom on its back controls it.
It often fights over territory with Shiinotic.

Il rpand des spores empoisonnes depuis son
chapeau. On peut les rcolter et les faire scher

Der Pilz auf seinem Rcken stt Giftsporen

natrliches Heilmittel verwerten.

La gran seta en su lomo dispersa esporas

remedios medicinales.

Sparge spore velenose dal fungo che ha
sul dorso. Se raccolte e fatte bollire, queste

It scatters toxic spores from its mushroom cap.
Once harvested, these spores can be steeped
and boiled down to prepare herbal medicines.

Linsecte est quasiment mort,  ce stade, et le
champignon est devenu le vritable cerveau.
Si on lte de son dos, il ne peut plus bouger.

Der Pilz auf seinem Rcken ist sein wichtigstes

sich ohne den Pilz nicht bewegen.

La mayor parte de su cuerpo est atrofiada,
excepto la seta del dorso, que controla al resto.
Si se desprende, Parasect ya no podr moverse.

La parte essenziale di questo Pokmon,
praticamente morto,  costituita dal fungo sulla
sua schiena. Se si stacca, non pu pi muoversi.

The bug is mostly dead, with the mushroom on
its back having become the main body. If the
mushroom comes off, the bug stops moving.

Des remdes traditionnels sont prpars avec
ses spores empoisonnes, mais ceux produits
 Alola seraient de moindre qualit.

Seine Giftsporen werden als natrliches
Heilmittel verwendet, doch bei Parasek aus
Alola ist die Qualitt etwas minderwertig.

Sus esporas venenosas se usan para elaborar
remedios medicinales que en Alola, al parecer,
son de calidad ms bien mediocre.

Dalle sue spore velenose si possono ricavare
dei farmaci. Tuttavia, sembra che quelli prodotti
ad Alola non siano di buona qualit.

Its poisonous spores are also used in traditional
medicine. Apparently, spores produced in Alola
are not of very good quality.
